Pre-Requirments 

Install ADB : https://www.xda-developers.com/install-adb-windows-macos-linux/
Install Android studio : https://developer.android.com/studio?gclid=CjwKCAjw1JeJBhB9EiwAV612y0lFrU0fsqZzWyX4CfoplPPJ-X0VgATx0PDOPKIU5-CKoKhzqPWAXRoCqKwQAvD_BwE&gclsrc=aw.ds
Create an emulator 
 Download the nykaa.apk (live) 
 Turn on the preprod vpn

download the .sh file from git : https://github.com/Nykaa/nykaa_automation/blob/master/scripts/monkeyRunner.sh
Save it to a location lets say "~/Desktop/Monkey/monkeyRunner.sh"
Open the terminal navigate to the loaction where file is saved : ~/Desktop/Monkey

Run the command for ubuntu : 
   source MonkeyRunner.sh <path_of_apk eg> <environment> <platform> : source MonkeyRunner.sh /home/sabhyatakaushik/Downloads/nykaaLive.apk prod nykaa and for Windows : Bash MonkeyRunner.sh <path_of_apk eg> <environment> <platform>
Result will be store in the directorywhere Monkey runner file is saved under the forlder name "MonkeyRunner" file name : currenttimestamp.log
For terminating the job : return command or CTRL+X or 
